These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: camping, video-games
Job: nurse, bartender
1. Job:nurse is in an even position##4
2. Job:bartender == Hobby:video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | video-games | camping |
| Job     | bartender    | nurse   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: cola, sprite
Sport: golf, basketball
1. Sport:golf is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left of Beverage:cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | cola        |
| Sport      | golf  | basketball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: country, r&b
Nationality: japanese, pakistani
1. Nationality:japanese is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left of Music-Genre:country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | country |
| Nationality   | japanese | pakistani |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
